theorem P1_iff_closure_eq_closure_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    P1 (X := X) A ↔ closure A = closure (interior A) := by
  constructor
  · intro hP1
    have h1 : (closure A : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior A) := by
      have : (A : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior A) := hP1
      exact closure_mono this
    have h2 : (closure (interior A) : Set X) ⊆ closure A := by
      have : (interior A : Set X) ⊆ A := interior_subset
      exact closure_mono this
    exact Set.Subset.antisymm h1 h2
  · intro hEq
    dsimp [P1]
    intro x hx
    have hx_closure : x ∈ closure A := subset_closure hx
    simpa [hEq] using hx_closure

theorem P2_interior_closure_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P2 (X := X) (interior (closure (interior A))) := by
  have h_open : IsOpen (interior (closure (interior A))) := isOpen_interior
  exact Topology.isOpen_implies_P2 (X := X) (A := interior (closure (interior A))) h_open
